block.command_block.10.command.1: Ragnarok... When wolves will swallow the sun and moon, when the stars will be snuffed and the land will be tremble. When the gods will face the tribes of the giants in a final battle, that will ravage all the nine worlds...
block.command_block.11.command.1: Of all creatures, only one does not fear Ragnarok - the evil god Loki... Bound deep into bowers of the earth by Odin himself. Only Ragnarok will set loki free to have revenge on gods and man alike... And it is only the power on Midgard of Odin and his Runestones that holds Ragnarok at bay...
block.command_block.12.command.1: All-father of the gods, Odin has always smiled upon the human race... To the most devout of his followers he entrusts stones inscribed with his personal Rune, a mark of his power in human world of Midgard. These Runestones are protected by only the most valiant of human warriors, until the day they die and are taken by the Valkyries to fight alongside Odin at Ragnarok.
block.command_block.15.command.2: There is a strange presence in my realm... a living presence... why, it's a mortal... a lone warrior... all alone... i should sent you some company, lone warrior...
block.command_block.16.command.2: The dead do not welcome the presence of the living, warrior... you remind them of all they have lost. And though you maybe strong, their numbers will take their toll... eventually
block.command_block.18.command.2: You see them, warrior? Odin will see the day he gave me so many subjects... now i send them to serve a new master, my father - Loki. The dark powers of his allies will transform these walking husks into the tools of our revenge... so many new dead, so very very many... each hour marks the passage of a thousand more throught these gates of the thousand more, thanks to that wonderful, bloodthirsty Conrack. Can you imagine destruction, warrior? Can you see how Midgrad will be ravaged once we unleash this horde?
block.command_block.20.command.2: Odin... One-eyed one? Father? Have you come at last to sent me free? Or you come to gloat upon my twisted form? No no no no... Odin, he does not forgive... And neither do i. You misbegotten old wretch! I will destroy you father... just like Baldr! I will! No! I am destroying your \"one-eye\" There are so many you discarded, forgotten, me, my daughter, These souls you condemned to her realm, dishonored, you called them. Not worthy of your Precious Valhalla... But they are great in number, and covered with my skin and with my blood, they will rise to crush Asgard itself!
block.command_block.21.command.2: You have the stench of the allfather about you, warrior... Perhaps you except Odin to lead you from my domain... I am the only of the living being he has captured into this cursed realm... And i has waited my release for a thousand years...
block.command_block.6.command.2: : Unbelievable! You killed all of the Loki's servants! Now it's time to meet with Loki, use the central Rune stone... good luck! May Odin be with you, brother!
block.command_block.9.command.1: From the birth the children of the north hear tales of the end of the world...
